21 SECTION 2.
22 Said subpart is further amended by revising Code Section 20-3-366, relating to repealer, as
23 follows:
24 "20-3-366.
25 This subpart shall stand repealed by operation of law on June 30, 2025 2029."
26 SECTION 3.
27 This Act shall become effective upon its approval by the Governor or upon its becoming law
28 without such approval.
29 SECTION 4.
30 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
